<section id="about" class="section">
  <div class="container">
    <h2 class="section-title">About Our Chapter</h2>
    <p class="section-subtitle">
      Discover how we're fostering the next generation of computing
      professionals through innovation, collaboration, and excellence.
    </p>

    <div class="about-grid">
      <div class="about-image">
        <img src="committee.jpg" alt="IEEE CS PDEU Team" />
      </div>
      <div class="about-content">
        <h3>Who Are We?</h3>
        <p>
          The IEEE Computer Society, Student Chapter at PDEU is a vibrant
          community dedicated to advancing technology and computing knowledge.
          As part of the world's leading organization for computer science and
          technology, we provide a platform for students to enhance their
          technical skills, professional development, and networking
          opportunities.
        </p>
        <p>
          Established in 2018, our chapter has grown to become one of the most
          active technical communities on campus, hosting various events,
          workshops, and initiatives that bridge the gap between academic
          knowledge and industry requirements.
        </p>

        <div class="about-stats">
          <div class="stat-card">
            <div class="stat-number">120+</div>
            <div class="stat-label">Members</div>
          </div>
          <div class="stat-card">
            <div class="stat-number">25+</div>
            <div class="stat-label">Events</div>
          </div>
          <div class="stat-card">
            <div class="stat-number">10+</div>
            <div class="stat-label">Workshops</div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  .about-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
    gap: 3rem;
    align-items: center;
  }

  .about-image {
    border-radius: 10px;
    overflow: hidden;
    box-shadow: 0 10px 30px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
  }

  .about-image img {
    width: 100%;
    height: auto;
    display: block;
  }

  .about-content h3 {
    font-size: 2rem;
    margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
    color: var(--primary);
  }

  .about-content p {
    margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
    line-height: 1.7;
    color: var(--dark);
  }

  .about-stats {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr);
    gap: 1.5rem;
    margin-top: 2rem;
  }

  .stat-card {
    background-color: white;
    padding: 1.5rem;
    border-radius: 8px;
    box-shadow: 0 5px 15px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.05);
    text-align: center;
    transition: var(--transition);
  }

  .stat-card:hover {
    transform: translateY(-5px);
  }

  .stat-number {
    font-size: 2.5rem;
    font-weight: 700;
    color: var(--primary);
    margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
  }

  .stat-label {
    color: var(--gray);
    font-weight: 500;
  }

  @media (max-width: 1024px) {
    .about-grid {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
      gap: 2rem;
    }
  }
</style>
